Class ErrorSummary

java.lang.Object
org.ivoa.dm.uws.ErrorSummary
All Implemented Interfaces:
org.ivoa.vodml.jpa.JPAManipulations, org.ivoa.vodml.jpa.JPAManipulationsForObjectType<Long>
@Entity @VoDml(id="uws:ErrorSummary", role=objectType) public class ErrorSummary extends Object implements org.ivoa.vodml.jpa.JPAManipulationsForObjectType<Long>
A short summary of an error - a fuller representation of the error may be retrieved from /{jobs}/{job-id}/error . objectType: ErrorSummary
